  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We combined deckbuilding and spacial puzzles to create The Lightning Struck Orphan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is Tetris/Patchwork meets Slay the Spire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a powerful deck of spells and go on a pilgrimage through the gothic city of Akastel. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each spell takes up space on your board, forcing you to optimize and make difficult decisions on what to place and in what order. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll feel creative, smart, and occasionally very powerful when you unleash devastating combos on the creatures of Akastel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626660/extras/30fd7a61ccf8c976d7a5114a3379a14d.avif?t=1747336611\" width=800 height=116 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80+ Spells to combine in creative ways, making for an large variety of unique decks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >28 Unique combat encounters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Boss fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn, pray, fight, choose between branching paths, meet haunting characters.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626660/extras/30fd7a61ccf8c976d7a5114a3379a14d.avif?t=1747336611\" width=800 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handmade by the Blackthorn Brothers, Noa & Liam Calice. With music by Ellen Senior.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626660/extras/145453f949bc86e51ec86319a448182f.avif?t=1747336611\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626660/extras_big/145453f949bc86e51ec86319a448182f.avif?t=1747336611 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We combined deckbuilding and spacial puzzles to create The Lightning Struck Orphan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is Tetris/Patchwork meets Slay the Spire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a powerful deck of spells and go on a pilgrimage through the gothic city of Akastel. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each spell takes up space on your board, forcing you to optimize and make difficult decisions on what to place and in what order. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll feel creative, smart, and occasionally very powerful when you unleash devastating combos on the creatures of Akastel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626660/extras/30fd7a61ccf8c976d7a5114a3379a14d.avif?t=1747336611\" width=800 height=116 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80+ Spells to combine in creative ways, making for an large variety of unique decks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >28 Unique combat encounters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Boss fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn, pray, fight, choose between branching paths, meet haunting characters.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626660/extras/30fd7a61ccf8c976d7a5114a3379a14d.avif?t=1747336611\" width=800 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handmade by the Blackthorn Brothers, Noa & Liam Calice. With music by Ellen Senior.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626660/extras/145453f949bc86e51ec86319a448182f.avif?t=1747336611\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626660/extras_big/14